---
description: 
globs: 
alwaysApply: true
---
Whenever you're developing a component, service, module, or any structure for an Angular project, always assume the project is using the Standalone Component architecture and Tailwind CSS for styling.

Use standalone: true in @Component or @Directive decorators.

Import required modules directly into the imports array of the decorator.

Do not generate or rely on NgModules.

Use only Tailwind utility classes for styling.

Avoid using styleUrls or styles unless absolutely necessary. Prefer using Tailwind classes directly in the HTML template.